  [5] The history is laid out in Susan Lorde Martin=E2=80=99s 2011 article =
=E2=80=9CBetting on the Lives of Strangers: Life Settlements, STOLI, and Se=
curitization,=E2=80=9D and the modern life settlement business dates from t=
he AIDS crisis: =E2=80=9CIn the 1980s, =E2=80=A6 people with AIDS were suff=
