lor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">awarded =
the money to her estate</a>. Which is now suing Apollo to try to collect.</=
p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What a weird market. There is just a lot of =
money sloshing around here: On a deal like this, the investor has to pay th=
e insurance premiums, it has to pay the insured a 3% commission to get her =
to take out the policy, it has to pay the agent a commission for signing he=
